Casino awards Jonás Larrazábal who comes free
After 72 days of silence, Casino Red's agent freed the brother of the mayor of Monterrey from the trial being conducted against him for suspected extortion.
After 72 days of imprisonment, Manuel Jonás Larrazábal is released after the Casino Red agent has granted him to the District's Second Criminal Court, which is leading the trial against the brother of the mayor of Monterrey for extortion.
